{"tid":994953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王岐山暗寸特朗普： 魔高一尺　道高八寸五","createTime":"2019-01-25T05:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T14:45:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"7537040c7bd2e2bebf6b3efa33fee9fa49c88151","tid":994953,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190125/20598560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F20598560&d=9P9Iq%2B49TWHZ5%2Bjigqrf1iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ac5fb869\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F20598560&h=ca1a5d9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190125/20598560</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月25日 <br />\n<br />\n王岐山暗寸特朗普：<br />\n魔高一尺　道高八寸五<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190125/large/a1502a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190125%2Flarge%2Fa1502a.gif&h=409af9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如何化解管治危機集中進行專題研討，為中共省部級高官首次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國國家副主席王岐山前日在瑞士達沃斯世界經濟論壇年會演講，不點名批美國貿易政策，又以「魔高一尺，道高八寸五」暗寸特朗普；王指世界經濟不能僅按發達國家或個別國家的安全標準，而世界經濟危機「是福是禍躲不過」，但未必會發生。對中國經濟，王坦言是樂觀派。<br />\n<br />\n王岐山在演講中稱，70年來中國發展取得矚目成就，許多外國朋友問他原因；他說歷史、文化和哲學考量是一把鑰匙，「要了解中國現實，就要了解中國的歷史，才能預見中國的未來」。王表示解決經濟全球化問題，須對症下藥，靠發展解決，「只能在做大蛋糕過程中，尋求更好地切分蛋糕的辦法，決不能停下來」。在與主持人對話環節，王談及世界經濟規則：「中國歷史上有句話叫『魔高一尺，道高一丈』，我說這話不對。舉個例子，嚴格意義上，警察永遠走在小偷後面。如果警察一直走在小偷前面，那麼世界上就沒有小偷了。監管和市場的關係也是這樣。所以應該修改這句話：『魔高一尺，道高八寸五。』」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：習認中共面臨七大風險學者：逢九必亂政權堪虞<br />\n<br />\n「是福是禍躲不過」<br />\n<br />\n被問到中國是否已為經濟危機做好準備，王岐山稱：「是福是禍躲不過，真發生危機又怎麼樣呢？」對中美關係前景，王的回答更簡潔：「中美經濟誰也離不開誰，這已是現實，結論就是互利共贏，鬥則兩傷，合則兩利。」美方沒參加這次達沃斯論壇。<br />\n<br />\n觀察者網  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n習認中共面臨七大風險 學者：逢九必亂政權堪虞<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n韓國瑜比武「招親」 贏家可與愛女嘆茶"},{"pid":"51c05c0603bee5650548c69f46458eb49eef20b0","tid":994953,"uid":29080,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"支那=魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8877753d1e479fadd3b24c1276411e257f1050df","tid":994953,"uid":184103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b3dcfc1446048bad8a1312fd8bf9fedea74407","tid":994953,"uid":121146,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"封左BING之後混身是膽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一於取消會面  直接打敗美國啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc25ce48552c4ffc85f470a457dca3af5c1189e9","tid":994953,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T05:46:55.000Z","msg":"一尺十寸喎<img src=\"/asset